### Executor 任务管理 HTTP 接口测试

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. 提交任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target_service": "test-service",
  "method": "processOrder",
  "args_json": "{\"order_id\": 123, \"user_id\": 456}",
  "max_attempts": 3,
  "priority": 0
}

### 2. 列出任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs?page_num=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. 获取任务详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. 更新任务参数（新增接口）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/args
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "args_json": "{\"order_id\": 999, \"user_id\": 888, \"updated\": true}"
}

### 5. 取消任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. 重新入队任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/requeue
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "run_at": 0
}

### 7. 查看任务执行历史
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/attempts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. 获取统计信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. 清理旧任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "succeeded_days": 7,
  "canceled_days": 30,
  "dead_days": 90
}

### 测试场景：验证更新参数的状态限制

### 场景1：更新 pending 任务的参数（应该成功）
# 先提交一个任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target_service": "test-service",
  "method": "testMethod",
  "args_json": "{\"test\": 1}",
  "run_at": 9999999999
}

###
# 记录返回的 job_id，然后更新参数
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/JOB_ID_HERE/args
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "args_json": "{\"test\": 2, \"updated\": true}"
}

### 场景2：尝试更新 running 任务的参数（应该失败）
# 需要有一个 running 状态的任务
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/RUNNING_JOB_ID_HERE/args
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "args_json": "{\"test\": 3}"
}
# 预期返回错误："running 任务不允许修改参数"

### 场景3：更新参数为非法 JSON（应该失败）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/args
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "args_json": "{invalid json"
}
# 预期返回错误："参数 JSON 格式不合法"

### 场景4：更新参数为空字符串（应该成功）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/args
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "args_json": ""
}

### 场景5：更新参数为空对象（应该成功）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/executor/jobs/1/args
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "args_json": "{}"
}
